    <h4><u>What are picklepoints?</u></h4>
    → Picklepoints are a measure of your interaction on this site. It's simple, the more you help others and add to the community, the more points you get.<br>
    → How many points do I get for commenting on a post or within a tournament? Good question:
    <ul>
      <li>Comments: <b>+2</b> PicklePoints</li>
      <li>Posts: <b>+4</b> PicklePoints</li>
      <li>Likes: <b>+1</b> PicklePoint</li>
      <li>Each Club Joined: <b>+3</b> PicklePoints</li>
    </ul>

    <h4><u>What do the colors around profile images stand for?</u></h4>
    <ul>
      <li><b><span style="color:gold;background:black">Gold:</span></b> A gold color around a user's profile image indicates that the user has created a 'Tournament' page and has/is looking for feedback.</li>
    </ul>
